#originalStanceText=At Conception
#originalTopic=when-does-life-begin
This is absurd.  Our laws are based upon the personal beliefs of the members of our society, past and present. Pursuant to Mr. O'Brien's theory, laws against slavery, murder, theft, child abuse, incest, polygamy, rape, etc., are all invalid.  There are people who believe those things are okay, so who are we to impose our beliefs upon them?Thankfully, our society has not disintegrated to this level.  